request.description:
Returns the health status of the service and its dependencies including database connectivity.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "status": "ok",
  "checks": {
    "mongodb": {
      "healthy": true,
      "message": "MongoDB connection is healthy"
    }
  }
}
```

**Status Codes:**
- 200: Service is healthy
- 503: Service is unhealthy (one or more checks failed)
